{"tid":1662402,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"幻想如果有平衡時空 香港會係點","createTime":"2019-10-18T17:40:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-19T00:39:09.000Z","uid":177406,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1dd34fff756a44383725196e1a2f0259eca0c880","tid":1662402,"uid":177406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T17:40:32.000Z","msg":"我希望平衡時空嘅香港 會係叫廣東省香港市 <br />\n<br />\n係呢個時空嘅香港 大家可以相約係煲底 一齊除低豬嘴面罩頭盔 迎接一個新嘅黃昏 唔洗再戴住泳鏡睇日落 大家嘅征途也能畫上句點 <br />\n<br />\n可能係一個自私想法 犧牲另一個時空嘅香港人 但可惜呢個時空嘅香港人 我相信係唔會因為任何事而放棄自己嘅理念與價值 <br />\n<br />\n追求嘅唔係錢同安穩 係自由與公義 <br />\n<br />\n我們就是被時代選中的孩子 我們就是注定要在極權統治下捍衛民主和自由的戰士  香港人呢段抗爭史 將會在歷史名冊上名留青史 成為現代對抗赤納粹的先驅 <br />\n<br />\n願我能在歷程的彼端與大家想見 而我相信那一天將會降臨  <br />\n<br />\n願榮光歸香港"},{"pid":"e8800cf6a09ff7f3bf9d5389e2b259e4bbb8af7a","tid":1662402,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T17:41:34.000Z","msg":"【日常文宣】[推爆佢]本土國際戰線&mdash;Facebook<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1662234\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1662234</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9e3675ddfcb32a909c7506c8acd5f5f30f2fd077","tid":1662402,"uid":146187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T17:42:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Agae3JH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAgae3JH.jpg&h=5afc0dbe&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NMyoW3J.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNMyoW3J.jpg&h=abdb81e4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wiMqqW3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwiMqqW3.jpg&h=c6e0d041&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Tfv3cB4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTfv3cB4.png&h=095e3dbf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3f33823f138953dd7db17e9de85bef218abf2934","tid":1662402,"uid":3549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T18:26:36.000Z","msg":"如果有平行時空 當年日本仔殺晒中國人<br />\n沒有中國人既世界會係點？"},{"pid":"7f94eef59aacc3a524ee1bf77500e0a0747405ff","tid":1662402,"uid":177406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3f33823f138953dd7db17e9de85bef218abf2934","tid":1662402,"uid":3549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T18:26:36.000Z","msg":"如果有平行時空 當年日本仔殺晒中國人<br />\n沒有中國人既世界會係點？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T00:39:09.000Z","msg":"當年十月革命沙皇贏咗 就唔會有共產黨"}]}